<item>
            <title>[LU-5835] Introduce the IOVEC in ptlrpc</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5835</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add IOVEC in the bulk descriptor for DNE 2. The current bulk transfer only supports page_vec, which is not enough for updates RPC, because some updates size might &amp;gt; 4K. For example linkEA, ACL etc, so we will add iovec to bulk transfer, and the buffer size of each vec can &amp;gt; 4k. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
